{"tid":952871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"億萬整容女東山再起 秀整形成果嚇壞日本網友","createTime":"2018-12-23T13:34:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T14:20:40.000Z","uid":212399,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"dd2389ae856a4f3d648364dffbe6bdf2813f17ed","tid":952871,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T13:34:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/12/21/99/5691454.png&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F12%2F21%2F99%2F5691454.png%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=14554c3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本「億萬整容女」拍影片展示整形成果，嚇壞眾多網友。圖片來源／YouTube<br />\n國外有許多女性因致力成為真人芭比而竄紅，但整形過頭的例子也層出不窮。一名日本女子過去因癡迷於整形而爆紅，沉寂多年後，日前被日本網友發現開始經營YouTube頻道。但影片一出，嚇壞許多網友，認為她整得太過頭。<br />\n據陸媒報導，Vanilla原本是素人，但因癡迷整形而登上網路媒體和電視節目，成為話題人物。她表示自己小學時性格內向，經常被同學欺負，當她回家向父親哭訴，父親一句話「你長得醜就要學會忍耐」，讓她決定將整形作為自己的人生目標。<br />\n為了籌措整形資金，Vanilla高中畢業就在酒店工作，並兼職平面模特兒。2013年，她參加日本電視節目《女人要看的事》（私の何がイケないの？）時，表示自己的整形次數已經超過一百次，共花掉一億日圓（台幣約2700萬元），因此獲得「億萬整容女」的稱號。<br />\n沉寂多年的Vanilla近期經營YouTube頻道，日前拍影片分享自己的整形成果，並說自己的整形花費目前已經超過兩億日圓（台幣約5400萬元）。但她的整形成果嚇壞許多日本網友，表示「縮圖太可怕我不敢按播放」、「這下巴可以殺人了」、「外星人嗎」、「根本恐怖片」、「以前還比較可愛」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SkYT-a3zkeM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSkYT-a3zkeM&d=fo1byzfTl6kaSqHZb4mTmHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=c7fca083\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SkYT-a3zkeM</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6810/3549866?from=udn-catelistnews_ch2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6810%2F3549866%3Ffrom%3Dudn-catelistnews_ch2&d=fo1byzfTl6kaSqHZb4mTmHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=830a77a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6810/3549866?from=udn-catelistnews_ch2</a>"},{"pid":"8d34cf707ce3dbd2440db41a898ec22aa5d3be8f","tid":952871,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T13:35:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cc436ad17e003c3224420142ccd69762053b845","tid":952871,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T13:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa897740810378f49303176408b1937790ed3f3","tid":952871,"uid":7741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T13:38:21.000Z","msg":"有無之前啲圖睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"252caec8617a51bcd9c64790af0030ae6d0d97f7","tid":952871,"uid":132587,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T13:38:25.000Z","msg":"父親一句話「你長得醜就要學會忍耐」<br />\n<br />\n多得佢老豆 細細個咁樣比屋企人直接話樣衰應該有陰影<br />\n所以唔怪得佢"},{"pid":"483959f0f805bc9d84879c853ab1d51d382de8a6","tid":952871,"uid":20867,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T13:39:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/53QACiz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F53QACiz.jpg&h=0e273d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9b2a67137bbfff1430b4003a677f25e22ec90fc","tid":952871,"uid":59711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T13:48:09.000Z","msg":"對眼好似隨時會跌出黎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a2d46347214f11c56d9eb026f75adc7b266229","tid":952871,"uid":78429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T13:59:29.000Z","msg":"之前唔係有節目安排佢同佢老豆傾下佢整容問題<br />\n佢老豆都唔記得自己有咁講過，仲話覺得整容前已經好靚不過都整成咁冇辦法"},{"pid":"d1dfedd088896df41b20da06bcf2f489c9842924","tid":952871,"uid":49664,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T14:04:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/11/05/1123946-XXL.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017